OL,3,CWinter Solstice: The shortest day of
OL,4,Cthe year has arrived
OL,6,FToday marks the winter solstice, which
OL,7,Fwill see the Northern Hemisphere
OL,8,Fexperience its shortest day of the
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FThe phenomenon may bring the most
OL,12,Fdarkness we've experienced all year
OL,13,Fround - but starting on Sunday, days
OL,14,Fwill get lighter and longer every day
OL,15,Funtil June.
