OL,3,CWinter Solstice: The shortest day of
OL,4,Cthe year has arrived
OL,6,FWhat is the solstice?
OL,8,FThe Earth's tilt is what gives us
OL,9,Fdifferent seasons, and means the
OL,10,FNorthern and Southern Hemispheres
OL,11,Fexperience winter and summer at
OL,12,Fopposite times.
OL,14,FEach hemisphere experiences winter
OL,15,Fwhen it is angled away from the sun,
OL,16,Fand moves into summer when it tilts
OL,17,Ftowards the sun.
